The paper discusses a new method for continuous authentication using wearable devices, which involves keystroke dynamics and sensor-based data acquisition. This topic is related to computer security (cs.CR), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), cybersecurity (cs.CY), signal processing (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
